Constructor Detail

Graph

public Graph(double nodeDensity,
             double width,
             double height,
             ConnectivityContract cc)
Graph nodes are constructed as to not be coincident. They are at least 1 away from eachother.

Parameters:
nodeDensity - Average nodes per unit
width - Width of the graph universe
height - Height of the graph universe
cc - Contract that specifies how the nodes are to be connected to eachother
